metadata.name: Avril15 if she were a dog.
metadata.description: This is my entry to the Avril15 contest of December 2022. I am Rosewolf, a 12 year old young artist. I have profound dyslexia and struggle with mainstream education so art is my escape. Creating this piece for Avril15 was a huge escape. and great fun. It is a 1/1 piece designed in Procreate.
